
This is for Mac installation guide.

1: check the mysql character and they should be utf8

K-MacBook-Pro:~ K$ mysql -uroot -p
Enter password: 
Welcome to the MySQL monitor.  Commands end with ; or \g.
Your MySQL connection id is 1319
Server version: 5.7.13 MySQL Community Server (GPL)

